  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  // PRODUCTION-CHAIN-II §F — CULTIVATED CROPS (sown by the `plant` job in a grow zone)
  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  // These never spawn naturally (empty `spawn.subterrains`). The plant job places one on a grow-zone
  // tile when the zone's seed matches `crop.seedItem` and the tile's soil tier ≥ `crop.minSoil`; it
  // then grows via the regrowth cooldown (`crop.growthTurns`, scaled by fertility × wetness at plant
  // time) until mature + harvestable. Reaping (harvest) routes to the `planting` labour. Annuals
  // deplete on harvest (replant); berries/herbs are perennial (persistent → regrow).
